CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1962, pg. A3, reads: "Easter Worshippers Add Frills to Faith - Mt. Ararat Baptist - The traditional Easter Sunday crowd which taxed the capacity crowd which taxed the capacity of Mr. Ararat Baptist Church and jams the stairway on the way out, presented a colorful picture of gorgeous spring togs. - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Women, men, and children, exiting Mt. Ararat Baptist Church after Easter services
